data.description: Waterfront Town Home Complex in central Niceville offers dock, boat slip and a beautiful sunset. This townhome has 3 bed 2.5 bath and includes nice tile floors as you walk into the foyer leading down the hall into the kitchen leading and wood laminate flooring for the living room. The unit has been remodeled to give you an open floor concept. The kitchen includes upgraded lighting, gray wood cabinets, granite countertops, and a glass backsplash. The living room has a large stone wood burning fireplace. All three bedrooms are upstairs, the master bedroom is on the back of the house and overlooks the spacious courtyard, docks, and Rocky Bayou. The guest bathroom has a nice size tile shower, wood vanity, and tile flooring. Bring your boat, paddleboard and fishing pole and enjoy the water!!
